## LDP

```
ldp Q, Q, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldp S, S, [X|SP {, #imm }]

ldp Q, Q, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldp W, W, [X|SP], #imm
ldp X, X, [X|SP], #imm
```

## LDR

```
ldr B, [X|SP], #imm
ldr H, [X|SP], #imm
ldr S, [X|SP], #imm
ldr D, [X|SP], #imm
ldr Q, [X|SP], #imm
ldr B, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr H, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr S, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr D, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr Q, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr B, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr H, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr S, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr D, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr Q, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr W, [X|SP], #imm
ldr X, [X|SP], #imm
ldr W, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr X, [X|SP, #imm]!
ldr W, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr X, [X|SP {, #imm }]
ldr S, <offset>
ldr D, <offset>
ldr Q, <offset>
ldr W, <offset>
ldr X, <offset>
ldr B, [X|SP, W|X {, UXTW|LSL|SXTW|SXTX { #imm } }]
ldr H, [X|SP, W|X {, UXTW|LSL|SXTW|SXTX { #imm } }]
```

## SUB

```
sub X|XSP, X|XSP, W {, UXT[BHW]|SXT[BHW] { #imm } }
sub X|XSP, X|XSP, X {, LSL|UXTX|SXTX #imm }
sub W|WSP, W|WSP, #imm {, LSL #imm }
```
